						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Broken hero-stone near the temple of Kallēśvara.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription records the grant of <hi rend="italic">nettarugeyi</hi> in recognition of the valour of <hi rend="bold">Asagara Sōmeya-Nyāka</hi> who died in a fight at <hi rend="bold">Hāveri.</hi> It belongs to the <hi rend="bold">13th century A.D.</hi></p>						

